# motivation

@symptom Sub-L's .resource schema canonicalized per-host nexus paths (ubu1=/home/aiden/Dev/nexus, ubu2=/home/summer/Dev/nexus, hetzner=/root/Dev/nexus, also /home/nexus mount; Mac=/Users/ghost/core/nexus). Parent-session smoke after kick_tree.hexa fix exposed a fleet of sibling tools still hardcoding `env("HOME") + "/core/nexus"` — these resolve to /home/aiden/core/nexus on ubu1 (DOES NOT EXIST), and similar non-existent paths on ubu2/hetzner.
